    "body": "Oh, I see, I thought you were talking about the validator in \"standalone\" mode.\r\n\r\nI think both configurations will be useful in production to different users.\r\n\r\nBeacon+Validator bundle:\r\n- less configuration -- easier config for single-validator users\r\n- potentially lower overhead rpc (if we write the memory rpc transport)\r\n\r\nBeacon independent of Validator\r\n- more flexible -- start/stop new validators independent of beacon node, use remote beacon node\r\n",
